n>Certainly, we&#8217;ll need energy. Humans need energy to survive and thr=
ive, and machines crave it even more desperately. The energy industry will =
be in good shape, assuming the AGI doesn&#8217;t crack the code to </span><=
a href=3D"https://substack.com/redirect/2f76d590-40b9-44da-a27e-0472a631b38=
