style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-s=
ize: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">That has implications in=
 the way you can run an exploration business. If you&#8217;re praying for a=
 single feasible deposit, it&#8217;s hard to invest in the future. If you&#=
8217;re planning to build a machine that prints new discoveries with high-c=
