olor: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px=
 0;"><span>During the Neolithic period, or </span><strong>Stone Age</strong=
><span>, early humans mined flint and stones for use in tools and weapons. =
