pan><strong>Aluminium</strong><span>, respectively, cheap and abundant.&#16=
0;</span></p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-heig=
ht: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Through most of those ages, humans mined lik=
