if you will. Roman loved the rocks, though, so he went, and he worked at th=
e mine for two months until his new employer told him the bad news: </span>=
<strong>they couldn&#8217;t afford to pay him for the work he&#8217;d done<=
/strong><span>.</span><strong> </strong><span>They would, however, pay for =
his trip back, the reverse of the odyssey he&#8217;d undertaken less than o=
ne fiscal quarter earlier.&#160;</span></p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 5=
5); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">But Roman wasn=
&#8217;t ready to go home yet. So he got on the phone and called everyone h=
