f he &#8220;Came over.&#8221; Easy. He took the ticket his old employer gav=
e him, exchanged it for the next flight to Vladivostok, spent the night sle=
eping in the Kamchatka airport (all the hotels were booked, but the airport=
 let you sleep there if you didn&#8217;t mind being locked in), woke up, an=
d headed off on his next adventure.&#160;</p><div class=3D"captioned-image-=
