</span></p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height=
: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Roman worked in the forest outside of Vladivos=
tok for a year. Work meant walking the area with a hammer and tools, lookin=
