liance, the explorer Legacy Minerals invited Earth AI to help discover depo=
sits at its Fontenoy site, and after 11 drill holes, it found a Palladium-P=
latinum-Gold-Copper-Nickel deposit.</p><div class=3D"captioned-image-contai=
