60;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26=
px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>Roman compared this early process as somethi=
ng like the early days of the hedge fund </span><a href=3D"https://substack=
