; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">The work has been worth it. Throu=
gh its series of twists and turns, Earth AI has landed on one of the most c=
ompelling business models I&#8217;ve come across.&#160;</p><h3 class=3D"hea=
der-with-anchor-widget" style=3D"-moz-appearance: optimizelegibility; -moz-=
