trong>Earth AI by the Numbers</strong></h3><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 5=
5); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Earlier, I gav=
e a simplified business formula for Earth AI:</p><pre style=3D"background: =
#eeeeee; border-radius: 8px; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 32px 0; paddin=
g: 16px; position: relative;"><code style=3D"font-size: 16px; font-weight: =
