alty streams because they&#8217;re low-margin fee-for-service businesses. E=
arth AI can.</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-h=
eight: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Explorers can&#8217;t invest in technolog=
